channel.title: Ctjabl
channel.description:
CTJABL (Cooler Than JABL) is my recent project. It's not completely finished, but class parsing is complete (reading attributes wasn't fun, even when I copied from BCEL). Here are the results of three tests: [code]Test # 1 CTJABL loaded scanner/ILScanner in 47 BCEL loaded scanner.ILScannerin 93
Test # 2 CTJABL loaded scanner/ILScanner in 46 BCEL loaded scanner.ILScannerin 109
Test # 3 CTJABL loaded scanner/ILScanner in 47 BCEL loaded scanner.ILScannerin 110[/code] I've modified my updater(s) to use this, and I no longer doubt the seemingly far-fetched speeds of pplsuqbawlz's library, because CTJABL can load all the RS classes in almost one millisecond each, and PSB is a good bit smarter than me.
Download: http://uppit.com/d/BR98K
EDIT: Updated, CTJABL can now fully dump a class too.
